out1 = r0 + r2*t1 - r1*t0a - r3*(t1*t0a)
out2 = r0 - r2*t1 + (r1 - r3*t1)*t0b  
     = r0 - r2*t1 + r1*t0b - r3*(t1*t0b)
out3 = r0 - r2*t1 - r1*t0b + r3*(t1*t0b)
```

